{"tid":1228320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"所有睇完太古巴打跳樓之後想結束生命嘅巴打入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-06-15T16:48:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T17:18:39.000Z","uid":145803,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2f067c339b4528be3d9a457645112878e15fcffc","tid":1228320,"uid":145803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:48:55.000Z","msg":"我知道連日嚟嘅事情的確為大家帶來好大壓力<br />\n導致情緒可能有啲不穩<br />\n再加上啱啱睇到太古嗰位義士跳樓重傷不治<br />\n衝擊之下都有犧牲嘅念頭<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但係</span></span><br />\n懇請各位留低條命<br />\n我哋仲有好多嘢等緊你哋做<br />\n送中條例而家都仲係暫緩㗎咋<br />\n距離真正嘅撤回十劃都仲未有一撇<br />\n太古烈士去咗我哋阻止唔到<br />\n但係淨低嘅其他巴打千祈唔好再做傻事<br />\n<br />\n留低條命仔<br />\n因為我哋真係好需要你<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">班賣港賊一日未死<br />\n我哋一日都唔可以死</span>"},{"pid":"f53b0ea13604c6cf5f4c5d24e816e81b65bf1eaf","tid":1228320,"uid":145803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:50:58.000Z","msg":"巴打們你哋仲有更加多嘢可以做<br />\n千祈唔好自殺"},{"pid":"5883b16833f5470fe7a9eba77da3a5bbf8c93f84","tid":1228320,"uid":145803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:53:23.000Z","msg":"如果依幾日開始意識到自已長期情緒緊張同走火入魔 請你抖一抖<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1212315\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1212315</a>"},{"pid":"c7eeaec9ac6f9cda53b91bcc4a46da4d88ad9e46","tid":1228320,"uid":145803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:55:23.000Z","msg":"推比多啲巴絲打睇到"},{"pid":"e6ecc378191d22bafca5af8b94759737b4fc9232","tid":1228320,"uid":145803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:58:03.000Z","msg":"[情緒問題]路難行，但有好多人一齊行緊<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1227912\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1227912</a><br />\n聽日出嚟同我哋一齊行"},{"pid":"6bc381d23533d80a9d7a7f4d06f185e9c989d1e1","tid":1228320,"uid":241614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:58:36.000Z","